Q&A: Favorite Hair and Our Skate League


PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

 

This week Kate and Leisha are answering your questions about their characters’ names, toxic relationships, who Shane is based on, and they get an update from a previous caller!
